# Optional harness sidecar

**Canonical agent policy is `AGENTS.md` only.** Do not treat this file, `.cursorrules`, or anything under `agent-harnesses/` as a substitute rulebook.

Optional collateral for batch/data-processing experiments (when explicitly relevant):

- `agent-harnesses/data-intensive/README.md`
- `agent-harnesses/data-intensive/config.json`
- `agent-harnesses/data-intensive/template.yaml`

If harness config conflicts with `AGENTS.md` → **AGENTS.md wins**. Stack gates stay pnpm-only (`pnpm 9`; never npm/yarn) per `.cursor/rules/03-stack-hard-gates.mdc`.
